QuestData.Title: Dog Food
QuestData.Description: <Dog whines as best as a lion seal can, feebly lifting one flipper toward his massive jaws.$B$BHe's hungry.$B$BThe Shelf of Mazu is covered in rockshell makrura that should make a fine meal for him.>

QuestData.CompletionText: <This has got to be the most pathetic lion seal you've ever seen.>
QuestData.RewardText: <Dog licks his chops happily, looking satisfied.>
